Package: iona-signer
Version: 28.7.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libssl3 (>= 3.0), adduser
Maintainer: IONA Engineering <packages@example.invalid>
Homepage: https://github.com/iona/iona
Description: IONA blockchain — mTLS remote signing server (v28.7.0)
 Standalone mTLS remote signer for IONA validators.
 Separates signing key from the main node process.
 Supports hot certificate rotation via SIGHUP.
 .
 Use with HSM/KMS or air-gapped signing machines.
